Mei Ru, 50, and her husband Song Ming, 53, were going shopping in Fuzhou, China .
Mr Song climbed out of the passenger side of the car and stood behind the car .
He then reversed, knocking him to the ground and backing up over his body .
CCTV footage shows Mr Song being rushed to hospital where surgeons battled to save him .
But he died from massive internal bleeding and broken ribs .